Hello,
 
Lots of T3 Turkey Reds for sale.  Most carry the rare No-Offer back.  Where ungraded, I’ve estimated (est) a potential PSA grade, but certainly can’t guarantee it.  There are some VERY nice and clean cards here.  I’m happy to send photos and more detailed descriptions of any or all.  Prices noted are net to me, PPFF is fine, as is a check/MO.  Shipping is on me.  PM, or email me at [url]craigdiamondt3@yahoo.com[/url].
 
Thanks for looking and Happy Collecting!
Craig
